    "lede": { "en": "A corner bracket on the frame carries a flexible gooseneck arm; the camera clips onto its tip and looks down over the phone bed, watching the screen.", "zh": "框架上的角支架固定一根柔性鹅颈臂，摄像头卡在臂端，俯视手机托架，监看屏幕。" }
