        "body": { "en": "The socket screw and hex nut that the gooseneck mounts on are 1/4-20 — the imperial tripod thread (≈ 6.35 mm). Don't substitute an M6.", "zh": "固定鹅颈臂的内六角螺钉和六角螺母是 1/4-20 规格，即英制三脚架螺纹（约 6.35 mm），不要用 M6 代替。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:130mm; top:120mm; width:70mm;"
